Description
BackEndUtility
This package contains the classes that are used to implement the backend of the application, including the enum classes and the input manager.

This package contains the classes that are used to calculate the metrics of the sellers and the buyers.
productClasses
This package contains the classes of the different types of products, and the classes that uses them.

This package contains all the product categories that inherit from the abstract class Product.
productClasses.Usages
This package contains the classes that are consistently used when interacting with products.
serializationUtil
This package contains the class that is used to serialize and deserialize the data of the application.

This package contains all the controllers used for the BuyerMenu.

This package contains all the classes related to the Seller's UI.

This package contains the main class of the application.
